social_posts.post_text:
Swingin' into the weekend like...😋
.
.
And...clinging to the few trees that still have color. Anyone have tree care advice for this lifelong Californian-turned-Tennessean? Why do some (maple) trees drop their leaves so much sooner than others? And can I help next year? I wanna keep all those colors longer!! 😅
.
.
Wishing you all a beautiful and blessed weekend! 💖

This AI trend is so interesting!! As an actress, being different characters is a part of my life... but this takes it to a whole new level! 😅 
.
.
I mean, I'm in a Impressionist seascape in #5! And #6 & #8 feel like illustrations you'd see on tarot cards (they don't really look like me though 😋). And the last one? "Barbie Madonna" for sure. 😅 But my favorites might be the first two. Do you have a favorite?
.
.
Thank you to the Lensa App for the fun. 🤗 Wishing you all a beautiful and blessed week! 💞

What a weekend!! Thank you to everyone at @thats4ent for a beautiful union of friends and fans; it's three days of so much love that it's hard to describe. We are so grateful to make these heartwarming movies, and to have our hearts warmed by YOU means the world. 🥰 These pics are just a small sampling of a weekend that would be difficult to capture in pixels! And scroll to the end for a BTS of me & @jonathandbennett attempting to look up and "find our light" for a flattering picture, haha! 
.
.
BTW, I had the privilege of watching the premiere of #TheHolidaySitter with @jonathandbennett and so many of my @gactv & @hallmarkchannel friends, all together, last night (see my instastories for video of that - my mom @mahailamckellar was with us, too!). What a beautiful film. I'm so proud of Jonathan - he's been telling me about this project for over two years and now it's in the world. It's full of love & kindness, so funny and so much heart. Yay! ❤️

Dollywood at Christmastime!! 🎄❤️🎄What an amazing time at an amazing place, and with some good friends. 🤗 Look, I love Disneyland as much as the next gal, but @dollywood has my heart - my favorite amusement park by far! (And not just because I shot a Christmas movie there 3 years ago. 😉) It's got this old timey feel, mixed with awesome roller coasters, shows and yummy food - even craftsmen there like blacksmiths, actually working! 
I didn't manage to capture the thrill rides (was too busy riding them!), but my favorite has to be Wild Eagle for sure. 😋 It was incredible to see a replica of @dollyparton 's childhood home - literally a 2-room structure with no running water or electricity. (See the 2nd to last slide.) But most of all, we loved the feeling just being there... like Dolly is giving you a big hug at every turn. ❤️
.
.
I can't wait to experience it in other seasons, too!
.
.
Have you been to Dollywood? If so, what's your favorite part??
.
.
Thank you, @Dollywood, for an unforgettable trip we hope to repeat soon. Merry Christmas, everyone!! 🎄❤️🎄

As many of you know, I can't get enough of holiday movies! 🎄 And as I start thinking about what my next Christmas movie might be, I thought I'd "visit" some of my favorite classics for inspiration... and I'm SO excited that these @warnerbrosentertainment classics are now available for the first time in 4K! 
.
.
Which one is your fav - Elf, Christmas Vacation, A Christmas Story or Polar Express? Merry Christmas, everyone! 🎄❤️

#WBPartner

BEST Christmas present EVER:
My 12-year-old learning Sleigh Ride, my favorite Christmas song!! 😭🎄❤️ Have a beautiful, blessed celebration. Sending you love from above that is yours, always. Merry Christmas! 🥰🥰🥰

Had the pleasure of celebrating this incredible human last night at his book release party! (Video in my instastories.) 😊 If you don't follow @loswhit yet - go check him out! Carlos is the beacon of light and unity this world needs, and I believe, craves. He'll make you smile and fill you with hope for humanity. And go get all his books - they will feed your soul! 🥰🥰🥰 Love you, Carlos!!

We met in 2013...and now it's 2023! I can't believe it will be a *decade* of being in love later this year! Just a shout-out to my amazing husband Scott. (I think it was National Spouse Day last week? 😅) This was a moment walking our dog together after church yesterday. Then we *finally* took down our Christmas decorations! A beautiful, simple Sunday together - appreciating every moment. 🙏🙏🙏 
.
.
Wishing you all a wonderful and blessed week ahead, filled with gratitude for what is right in front of us - may we never take our gifts for granted, whatever forms they take. 🤗

Happy 35th Anniversary to The Wonder Years! 🎉 On January 31st, 1988, we premiered on @abcnetwork immediately following the Superbowl, and my life would be forever changed. I'm so grateful for the incredible memories, but even more grateful for all of you who have followed my career from that heartwarming, family tv show to the heartwarming movies I feel so fortunate to make today on @gactv ❤️.
.
.
I love that, unlike 35 years ago, we have opportunities to connect through social media! 🤗 And I can't wait to meet some of you in CT at @thats4ent 90's Con this March, where we'll be celebrating The Wonder Years and I'll be signing autographs for you alongside @realdanlauria & @oliviadabo, who played the dad & sister on the show. 🥰
.
.
One of my favorite things is hearing about how families watched the show together. Would love to hear your favorite memories of The Wonder Years - favorite episode or scene or whatever! Let the nostalgia begin. 💕💕
.
.
#TheWonderYears #anosincríveis #losañosmaravillosos #childhoodmemories 💕

Apparently it's National Periodic Table Day! 🧪 So a here's a 2021 #TBT of me and my son performing "The Elements," a 1959 song by Tom Lehrer that includes all 102 chemical elements of The Periodic Table known at that time. In case you were wondering, yes, I sped it up a touch, to keep it under 1 min. And.. in case you'd like to sing along... 😋
.
.
🎵 There's antimony, arsenic, aluminum, selenium,
And hydrogen and oxygen and nitrogen and rhenium,
And nickel, neodymium, neptunium, germanium,
And iron, americium, ruthenium, uranium,
Europium, zirconium, lutetium, vanadium,
And lanthanum and osmium and astatine and radium,
And gold, protactinium and indium and gallium,
And iodine and thorium and thulium and thallium.
.
There's yttrium, ytterbium, actinium, rubidium,
And boron, gadolinium, niobium, iridium,
And strontium and silicon and silver and samarium,
And bismuth, bromine, lithium, beryllium, and barium.
.
There's holmium and helium and hafnium and erbium,
And phosphorus and francium and fluorine and terbium,
And manganese and mercury, molybdenum, magnesium, dysprosium and scandium and cerium and cesium. And lead, praseodymium, platinum, plutonium, Palladium, promethium, potassium, polonium, and tantalum, technetium, titanium, tellurium,
And cadmium and calcium and chromium and curium.

There's sulfur, californium, fermium, berkelium,
And also mendelevium, einsteinium, nobelium,
And argon, krypton, neon, radon, xenon, zinc, and rhodium, and chlorine, carbon, cobalt, copper, tungsten, tin, and sodium.

Happy #nationalperiodictableday ! #chemistry #homeschooling #periodictable #tomlehrer #theelements

Beyond thrilled to be developing my #GreatAmericanChristmas 2023 movie for you all! 🎄❤️🎄 This movie, Royal Christmas Ball, is extra special to me because it's the first one I helped to write the story for, and it's my first dance movie. 💃 Coincidence? And I'm incredibly grateful to billabbott and everyone at @gactv & @mpca_bktv 🤗. Can't wait to share more later this year! 
.
.
.
What are you the most excited for in a Christmas movie?? 🎄❤️🎄

What a birthday weekend! 💕 Happy birthday to my wonderful, loving, supportive, all-around awesome husband, Scott! We celebrated in many ways - from a fancy dinner and impromptu photo shoot with a very cool display of antique phone booths (!) to exploring the caves of the underground Ruby Falls and wandering the Fairyland Caverns of Rock City... always such a fun time! Here's to another trip around the sun, my love! I love you! ❤️

.
Wishing you all a wonderful week ahead, filled with all sorts of adventures to be grateful for. Hugs to you all! 🤗

After a beautiful morning at church, it was a beautiful day for a bike ride! 🚲🌞 Sending blessings to every single person reading this today. ❤️ May we always remember to appreciate the little things...🙏 I've lived long enough to understand that those *are* the big things. 😉
.
.
Happy Sunday! 🤗❤️🙌

#blessings #nature #familytime #messyhairdontcare 😋

Happy Palm Sunday! 💕 Today is a very special day for me: It marks my one year anniversary of the beginning of my Faith Journey. 🌟 On Palm Sunday 2022, my friend @candacecbure brought me to her church's Passion Play, and I had an experience I'll never forget and that changed my life in a way I can't even begin to describe. But its profound effect has stayed with me. 
.
.
That JOY that bubbles up without explanation other than it extends from connection to the Holy Trinity - I wish that profound feeling of love and peace for each and every one of you. 🙏❤️🙏

Happy Easter!! What a beautiful service this morning celebrating the miraculous resurrection. 💕💕 
.
.
.
Grateful to be with lots of family on Easter today! (Pictured here with my 12-year-old son, who is starting to look like a teenager, and my 73-year-old dad...who still looks a little like a teenager. 😋)

Loving our new Great American Spring attire!! @gactv 💕 When's the last time you got up and danced just for fun, even just by yourself at home? (Hint: it's worth it and feels great!) 
.
.
Wishing you all a beautiful and blessed weekend, full of flowers and impromptu dance parties. 🌸💃

#TBT Earth Day 1992! 🌏 And this 90s vibe is strong...😅 Side part ✔ Fanny pack ✔ Baggy sweatshirt ✔
Yes, my sister Crystal was Becky Slater on The Wonder Years. 🥰
.
.
.
🐳 Earth Day fun fact: Did you know that whales dive deep to get their food, which is rich in elements not found near the surface? Then their element-rich poop becomes a powerful fertilizer for photo plankton!
And we sure want healthy and plentiful photo plankton - not only are they the very bottom of the food chain - the basis for all life (!) - but they also absorb TONS of carbon dioxide from the air. So not only are whales incredibly majestic, they keep all of life thriving. Marine royalty and proper stewards of this planet. 🥰 So many reasons to protect these beautiful creatures. ❤️❤️❤️
.
.
Happy Earth Day! 🌎
.
.
#EarthDay2023 #90sfashion #whales #TheWonderYears #anosincríveis #losañosmaravillosos

RIP to the iconic backbone of @dancingwiththestars, Len Goodman. He was so gracious to me during my time on that show. My thoughts and prayers are with his family - and his extended #DWTS family. 🙏 
.
.
Such strange timing - this happens to be my first day of dance rehearsals for my @gactv dance movie, "Swing into Romance." Len, thank you for everything you have been to the dance world, and I'll do my best to make you proud. 💕💕

Where am I and what is the meaning of this tropical cocoa?? 🏖🎄
.
.
I'm shooting a super fun "Christmas in July" promo for @gactv and @dishnetwork! (Which isn't at ALL confusing for me in April. 😅) If you have Dish, you'll see me with this awesome concoction on your TVs this June & July! 😋
.
.
Wishing you a beautiful day in April...it's April, right? 😅

How's it going, friends? Hope you're feeling peaceful today. I'm feeling so grateful for this experience of shooting my latest @gactv movie. One week down, two to go. Hard work but just so gratifying. Can't wait to share details soon.
.
.
Sending you all a hug and wishes for a beautiful and blessed Sunday! 🙏

A different kind of Mother's Day this year...no fancy brunch with flowers, no getting dressed up or putting on makeup... instead, a 3-hour virtual hang with my munchkin as I'm up here in Canada shooting my @gactv movie. But you know what? It was awesome. Feeling so grateful and excited to give him a squeeze very soon! ❤️❤️❤️
.

No matter your situation, I hope you felt love and peace in your heart yesterday. 🕊🙏

#nomakeup #mommysontime #happymothersday❤️

And... that's a wrap on my very first @gactv #FallHarvest (dance!) movie, "Swing into Romance"! 🍁🎬💃 I'm so grateful to every single person involved in this production. 👊 What an incredible experience, and I can't wait to share the joy with you this September...! In the meantime, I'm wishing you all a beautiful week ahead, and don't forget  to dance, my friends. 💃🎵🕺
Beautiful morning at church today with incredible worship. Wishing all of you a blessed Sunday!! 💕💕

1 or 2? 😋 #trailerselfie
.
.
My good friend @benjaminayres has started an inspiring mini-movement called @romance__university, rallying rom-com fans and raising over $11K (so far) for women's shelters like @anduhyuan @streethaven87 @alexandriahousela, and proceeds from every purchase will continue to be donated. 🙏 He told me this: "The intention behind the project was to continue building community within the RomCom world and let fans decide upon designs and products. It’s a beautiful collaborative little creative world."
.
.
Great job, @benjaminayres !! Link to store at romance-university.com in my instastories. 🙌🙌

Christmas Con, let's do this!! 🥰 So many great memories from the last one, and I can't wait to meet so many of you in Kansas City tomorrow & Saturday at this fantastic event to celebrate these magical Christmas movies I'm so grateful to be a part of (and then I leave to shoot my next one for @gactv! 🥰). Still need tickets? Check out the link at @thats4ent - see you there!! ❤️🎄❤️

Incredible time at another incredible @thats4ent extravaganza!! It fills my heart to reconnect with friends and to connect with all of you - who we make these movies for. 💕🎬
Thank you for having me, and thank you to all the fans! Can't wait to do it all again at 90s Con in September and Christmas Con in December!! 🎄❤️🎄

Ha! 34 years ago this week - June 10-16th, 1989 - this was the cover of TV Guide. I remember NOT understanding the decision behind those swirly-patterned capri pants they gave me to wear. 😅 And fun fact: we were sitting on a horizontal tree trunk (from a living tree). 
.
.
And... in case you weren't aware - this week (this year!) marks the season 2 premiere of the re-imagining of The Wonder Years - check out these accounts to learn more! @wonderyearsabc @saladinpatterson  @dulehill 
.
.
Hope you're all having a WONDER-ful week! 😉🤗
One way I attempt to look fresh & youthful in my @gactv Christmas movies? Yep, eyepatches all over my face in my trailer at lunchtime. 😅 (That, and eating clean! 😋) #themoreyouknow

A beautiful, hot summer day! Me, comfortable in my trailer. Also me, about to step outside, bundled up to shoot my Christmas movie. 😅🥰
.
.
Feeling incredibly blessed to have the opportunity to make such Christmassy joy on a @gactv movie, no matter what the season. ❤️🎬🎄(More in my instastories.) Hope you all have a beautiful and blessed weekend, my friends! 🤗

What a beautiful and blessed 4th of July! 🇺🇸🎉 Feeling so grateful for family, friends, and the incredible gift of living in this country with freedoms that were hard-earned centuries ago... and continue to be. 
❤️
I am wishing you all a wonderful week ahead filled with gratitude for what we have, an awareness of all the important things in life worth fighting for, and the courage to build unity across the many diverse points of view on *how* to preserve this great nation. 🇺🇸🇺🇸🇺🇸

It's July, and that means Great American Christmas in July is happening right now on @gactv! And for a Christmas-in-July gift 😋, Great American Family is available to all @dishnetwork customers this month! Tune in now on DISH Channel 165. See you there! 🎄🎬❤️

Thrilled to announce details for my new @gactv Christmas movie! 🎄🎬❤️ The dashing @damonrun and I costar in "A Royal Christmas Romance," debuting this Thanksgiving weekend. Thank you to @parademag and @bethebuddha for the exclusive announcement - link in my instastories! 🎉
.
.
.
#ARoyalChristmasRomance @billabbotthc @slaymemedia @galivingtv @pureflix @sptv @mpca_bktv @danselmo6

Mama's in vacay mode...! 😋 After two back-to-back movies, it's time to chill and recharge with family... 😎 
But, um, can somebody please tell me what is up with my face in the last shot with Draco? Like a cartoon frog or something, right?? 😅 
See my instastories (and threads!) for more vacay shots. Also... any guesses where we are? Hint: it's tropical! 🌴
.
.
#familytime #vacation #nomakeup #nomakeupselfie #relaxed #messyhairdontcare

Thrilled to announce my costars for my Autumn Harvest @gactv movie, #SwingIntoRomance - @davidhaydnjones & @glebsavchenkoofficial - yes, from @dancingwiththestars - October 7th! 🤗
.
.
The uber-talented and charming David Haydn-Jones and I did a Christmas movie together in 2016, and it was awesome to work with him again in Swing Into Romance! Our chemistry is great, and I was so impressed at how much dance he learned in a very short amount of time. 
.
.
And it was SUCH a joy to relive the thrill of my time on Dancing with the Stars with the incredible Gleb Savchenko. The really cool and unique part was that we were mentors to each other: Not only did he mentor me in dance, but this was first acting role, so I had the great pleasure to mentor him in acting! We would alternate between dance rehearsals and acting rehearsals over the weekends. He was like a sponge with everything I taught him and did a terrific job playing my ex-fiancé and ex-dance partner - you'd never know it was his first acting job. And dancing with him is some of the most fun I have ever had on a movie set! (Yes, I dance with both David and Gleb in this movie. 🤗)
.
.
David, Gleb, and I like to refer to our time together in Canada as "Art Camp." It was Acting Camp for Gleb and Dance Camp for me and David. A treasured time for sure. 🥰 So excited to share this movie with you October 7th on Great American Family channel!! 💃🕺

Sneak peek at a monitor shot from one of the dance sequences I got to do with @glebsavchenkoofficial in my upcoming #AutumnHarvest @gactv movie, #SwingIntoRomance! Can't wait till I can share the entire movie with you in September! 🥰💃🕺

Costa Rica photo dump!! 🌴✈️🐸🌊 My family and I had a wonderful time and many adventures! Swimming, snorkeling, waterfalls, horseback rides, rainforest walks (that tree frog looks like a National Geographic - but that was taken on my phone!), and more. And that very last shot at the waterfall? Shout-out to @glebsavchenkoofficial for teaching me dance arms - if you wanna get better at something, you practice wherever you are! 😋 
.
.
We took some pics & video on my husband's underwater camera so once I get those, there might be a part two. 😉
.
.
Super grateful for the opportunity to make new family memories in a cool new spot, and I'm wishing you a week of making beautiful memories, whether on adventures, or right at home. ❤️

The family that works out together... 😋🤗💪 Big thank-you to my good friend @melissajoanhart for organizing such a fun group workout this morning (with so many dear friends!) at her husband @mmwilkerson 's brand new @bft_studios this morning. It was great to exercise & sweat with family & friends. Really fun class! 
.
.
This was a pretty hard-core experience, but I've found that any amount of gentle exercise or even stretching really helps circulation and can feel great!! 
.
.
Tell me below - how do you squeeze in fitness, even if just for 10 min?? #healthyhabits 🙌

#FBF to working out... on vacation! Costa Rica was great but SO hot & humid, and the ocean & pool were also super warm... so some days we feel pretty sluggish, wanting to just sorta lie around. 😅 But my body got so antsy & knew it needed to MOVE, so the air-conditioned gym was such a blessing! And man oh man - always SO happy after a workout. That circulation moving, the endorphins flowing. 
.
.
Somebody please tell me: Why is it often so hard to motivate to do something that we KNOW we'll be so glad that we did??

Just a fun, live hang! And midway through, I shared the topic of one of my @greatamericancommunity videos - a short examination of The Lord's Prayer and some EZ quotes that help me with forgiveness. For a more summarized version of that topic, check out my videos at the link in @greatamericancommunity's bio!

Hiiiii! I am smiling at you and sending you love, yes, YOU, beautiful human! 🥰🙏💖
Tell me, what are you looking forward to the most this week?? ⬇️
.
.

So blessed to have family in town for Labor Day weekend and waking up early for the 8am church service this morning! 🙏 My dad & brother here from San Diego and my sister from San Francisco. 🥰❤️🤗 
.
.
Yes, my sister Crystal played Becky Slater on The Wonder Years. And no, we didn't all intentionally color-coordinate our outfits. 😅
.

Wishing you all a beautiful Sunday! 💖

How is my baby boy 13?? 😭 It's taken me two days to post this, and it's funny how we try to capture our child's spirit in a series of pictures like this - impossible, but we still try. 😋 
Draco, I'm SO PROUD to be your mother and feel incredibly privileged to be a part of your growth from baby to kid to teenager...and soon enough, young man!! I love you SO MUCH!

The latest duo on @dancingwiththestars?? 😋 Not quite - but I had to wish the incredible @glebsavchenkoofficial a very Happy 40th Birthday!! And what better way than to celebrate him in his first acting job that I recently had the honor of acting & dancing with him in (which I can't explicitly promote due to the strike). But let me just say this: Gleb, you've got a bright future ahead as an actor. 👊 And as you embark on this new decade, I hope you are super excited about this new aspect of your already glittering career, superstar! 🌟🤩💫

Such an amazing weekend celebrating the 90's with so many fellow child actors 😁 and meeting so many incredible people!! Thank you to everyone who shared your stories with me. You touched my heart, for real!! And HUGE thank you to everyone at @thats4ent for creating such an impactful experience for so many. 🥰🥰🥰 See you in New Jersey for Christmas Con this December! 🌟 #90sCon

In honor of tonight's premiere of @dancingwiththestars , here's a BTS dance rehearsal clip of me & @glebsavchenkoofficial (as seen on @usweekly last week!) from our upcoming project. 💃🕺🍁🎬 Made me feel like I was on @dancingwiththestars again! 🥰
.
.
Dance brings SO much joy, but I know how nerve-wracking that first DWTS live show is for the contestants 😁 - although my season was in 2014 (with the awesome @valentin !), I remember it like it was yesterday!! 
.
.
Best of luck to ALL the pros & contestants, and most of all - ENJOY!! I'll be watching. 🌟

You guys!! Just 3 days until "Swing into Romance" makes its world premiere on @gactv !! I'm beyond proud of this movie, for so many reasons... first, I got to practice my @dancingwiththestars skills with two awesome partners - @davidhaydnjones (who was also my incredible co-star!) and DWTS pro @glebsavchenkoofficial, which was a dream come true!! 💃🕺 Also, this was @glebsavchenkoofficial 's first acting job - and after all the work he put in (I had the joy of coaching him!), you'd never know he hadn't been doing it for years. 🤩 And finally, the story for this movie was first conceived by my amazing husband, Scott Sveslosky- you'll see his name in the credits! 🎉
.
.
BTW, for those who are tracking the strike: I just heard from our wonderful production company that they secured an interim agreement which allows for promotion. I'm incredibly grateful to SAG-AFTRA president Fran Drescher for providing the option of these interim agreements. 🙏 I've seen her say they are an important part of her strategy for getting big studios on board, and that actors are encouraged to support those projects. 💪 And I continue to be hopeful for a positive resolution SOON to this strike so Hollywood can get back to work - under fair conditions! 🙏

What a #TBT reunion it was at @dancingwiththestars this week - and brought back so many memories! My old partner @valentin - it was so great to see you again. Thank you for the intense training in our season (9 years ago!). My "new partner" @glebsavchenkoofficial - SO excited to show the world our movie #SwingIntoRomance this Saturday on @gactv ! 💃🕺 
.
.
And so great to see @markballas (who danced with my dear friend @candacecbure in my season!) and his wife @bcjean - two of the most talented people!! 
.
.
Omg, @therealalfonsoribeiro - you are killing it as the host - I'm so friggin proud of you!! Loved catching up with old & new friends @mrsangelaribeiro1 @therealkateflannery & @tiacarrere , and sharing the whole experience with my son and my mom @mahailamckellar 
.
.
Thank you @deena_katz and everyone at DWTS for an awesome night and for making me feel like a part of the family after all these years! 💃🕺💖

Had a blast visiting @glebsavchenkoofficial at @dancingwiththestars this week and getting excited about our movie!! Catch us Saturday Oct 7th at 5pmPT/8pmET on @gactv along with my awesome costar @davidhaydnjones in our new movie #SwingIntoRomance ! 💃🕺🎬 And I'm excited to live tweet with you all! 🥰

TONIGHT'S THE NIGHT!! I couldn't be more thrilled to share this movie with you, #SwingIntoRomance! 💃🕺🎬 And I'll be live tweeting (X'ing? 😅) during the premiere on @gactv at 5pmPT/8pmET - so I hope you'll join in the fun! 🤗
.
.
This movie combines two of my passions, acting and dance, and I'm humbled by the talent that made this movie a reality, at every stage. @billabbotthc - thank you for believing in this project from the beginning - also everyone at @gactv, @mpca_bktv and @danselmo6 for making it a reality. Thank you to our director @b_radleywalsh and the entire cast & crew. David - your willingness to throw yourself into swing dance training with all the gusto that makes you who you are - well, it was awesome to witness, and you killed it!  And Gleb - what an incredible partnership we discovered of coaching each other! 🤗 I'm grateful for your choreography and all your guidance and training, and I'm thrilled to have had the privilege of ushering in your acting career. 🌟
.
.
Thank you for tuning in, and enjoy the movie, everyone! It's a great time that will have you on your feet, cheering and feeling fantastic. 🤗🌟
.
.
Have you ever done any swing dancing, salsa or ballroom of any kind? Tell me in the comments, and LET'S HAVE A DANCE PARTY - comment with a GIF below - search @danicamckellar to find lots of fun dance GIFs from the movie (made by the talented @izzyink!)

My LIVE chat with @glebsavchenkoofficial today!! So much fun to catch up with this superstar (and costar for my movie tonight #SwingIntoRomance!) - watch or listen like you would a podcast and hear us talk about DWTS, working together on dance AND acting, and our premiere tonight! 🌟
.
.
**Scroll to 9:30 to see where Gleb joins me!*
.

LIVE TWEET with both of us tonight at 5pmPT/8pmET and tune in for the premiere of #SwingIntoRomance on @gactv ! 💃🕺🎬

Exactly 10 years ago, Scott and I met and ever since, I've felt like the luckiest woman on the planet!! 🥰 October 16, 2013, we met for coffee, which turned into lunch, which turned into frozen yogurt, which turned into a lifetime together! 🎉🎉🎉
Thank you Scott, for being the best husband and partner I ever could have dreamed off. I love you so much and all our adventures together. Here's to many more decades ahead! ❤️ Happy 10 year anniversary of our first date!!

In honor of tonight's Disney Night on @dancingwiththestars, here's a throwback to nine years ago, when I got to dance the Quickstep with @valentin to Beauty and the Beast's "Be Our Guest"! 🌟 Good luck to all the couples tonight!! 
.
.
What's your favorite Disney cartoon movie?? For me, it's a three-way tie between The Little Mermaid, Beauty and the Beast, and Cinderella! 💖🤗

Happy 50th anniversary to @inventorshof! 🥂 (Tell me your favorite invention below! ⬇️) I was truly honored to host the National Inventors Hall of Fame Induction Ceremony on Thursday - with Mo Rocca this time - to celebrate brilliant minds behind some of the world's most groundbreaking inventions at "The Greatest Celebration of American Innovation." 🤗 
.
.
Swipe through for pics and a video my husband took of me on stage 😋 - just a small sampling of the night. And a video I grabbed of amazing wheelchair-bound US Army veteran Rory Cooper ballroom dancing with his wife...💃👩‍🦽 and guess what? He just so happens to be the inventor of the lightweight wheelchairs (plus all sorts of adaptations he masterminded) that allows this kind of mobility - he began by building prototypes in his mom's auto repair shop when he returned from serving back in the early 1980's. 🤗🇺🇸 For more stories like this and also those of fellow inductees like Lynn Conway, Marjorie Stewart Joyner, and Lonnie Johnson (swipe for a pic of us!), check out invent.org. 🙌
.
.
From the youngest innovators (see slide with me & little Jalani on stage and then with his family at the after party!) to the most accomplished, it's inspiring to see how @inventorshof supports every step of the innovation journey. It was a privilege to help celebrate 50 amazing years of this nonprofit along with @uspto and to see the full circle of its impact, starting with invention education programs for kids like @CampInvention - which Jalani participated in last summer. 🥰 I encourage you to check out @inventorshof and @campinvention. 🔬
.
.
Now tell me, what's your favorite invention of all time?? Maybe something you use every day and maybe that we all take for granted? 😁 
.
.
.
#NIHF2023 #NIHF #NIHF50Years #Innovation #HallOfFame #InventionEducation #STEMEducation #CampInvention

Happy New Year, everyone!! Let's make it a year of renewed commitment to taking care of ourselves - lots of water, healthy food, moderate exercise - nothing crazy, just all the things we know are good to do. Because you know what? When we take care of our bodies, our bodies take care of us - including our mood! It's a great investment in ourselves - and you are worth the effort!! 🤗 (I'll be doing more yoga and stretching this year - it feels SOOO good and it so important for our bodies to function properly - link in my bio for my yoga DVD, "Daily Dose of Dharma." ❤️)
